title: Release 1.6
message:
Release 1.6
Updated manifest and update text strings.xml

Signed-off-by: Bram Havers <bramhavers@gmail.com>

title: Fixed:
message:
Fixed:
- crash (npe) on startup when no thinking rock file is selected
- crash (npe) on starting voice recognition when not installed on device
- crash (npe) when sending email and no topic is selected

title: Updates:
message:
Updates:
- Automatic periodic synchronization (see Preferences).
- Improved last synchronization information
- Fixed incorrect time indication

Signed-off-by: Bram Havers <bramhavers@gmail.com>

title: Beta3
message:
Beta3
- Automatic periodic synchronization.

- Improved last synchronization information

- Fixed incorrect time indication

title: Cleaned up Dropbox.download method, included hash checken to not
message:
Cleaned up Dropbox.download method, included hash checken to not
download a file if it has been not been changed. Included message to
follow status of download process. Moved download progress constants
from MainActivity to Dropbox. Included force download switch.

title: User friendly last uptime date/time in main screen
message: User friendly last uptime date/time in main screen

title: - Fixed timezone bugs (last sync label on home screen
message:
- Fixed timezone bugs (last sync label on home screen
showed incorrect time, and actions showed wrong time).
- Started to make last sync label on home screen more friendly
(shorter), needs more improvements.
